        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The &amp;quot;Passenger Vehicle/Loading Vehicle Loan Scheme&amp;quot; introduced by the Social Justice and Empowerment Department, Gujarat, aims to provide financial assistance in the form of loans to unemployed individuals belonging to Scheduled Caste Antyodaya families, enabling them to purchase passenger or freight vehicles and thereby create self-employment opportunities in the transport sector. The scheme is being implemented by the Dr. Ambedkar Antyodaya Development Corporation.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n  - Financial assistance in the form of a loan.\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The \"Passenger Vehicle/Loading Vehicle Loan Scheme\" introduced by the Social Justice and Empowerment Department provides financial support to unemployed individuals from Antyodaya Caste for purchasing passenger or freight vehicles. \n",
